    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood of the species Mesua ferrea, native to Burma. It is a tough, hard wood, typically used for making furniture, cabinetwork, and inlay.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
